{"tid":1377671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解決運動失焦既方法","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:50:39.000Z","uid":55627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8645bae9ee79c7e5f3e044360d9fc117803b6f2d","tid":1377671,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"係用連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n每個星期18 區搵一個標誌性地標. 即刻將佢連儂化<br />\n不要放棄5 大訴求, 不可失焦<br />\n要深入居民宣傳<br />\n現在每個星期都送頭, 林奠唔出聲, <br />\n個個星期比狗打, 根本係送血, 無腦既港豬只會怪你地阻住晒<br />\n每個星期幾萬人去連儂化一個地方, 不停將一個訊息講完又講, 講完再講<br />\n<br />\n你地有無留意之前有一條宣傳某垃圾手遊game 既片. 其實無介紹到有幾好玩, 佢只係將同一條訊息係咁重覆, 就會入腦<br />\n<br />\n係呢啲膠著既時候, 係要另辟道路, 唔可以再挨打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ba2bccd4217d6ce9eafd16f3453073caac6fef","tid":1377671,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"9405a51f28efe4bfa7ed219601cf00f1a53b7fe7","tid":1377671,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有罷工，可以停止每星期流血衝突！</span></span>"},{"pid":"04511772b4d9dfa5055daba756b1382a20e77ab0","tid":1377671,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9405a51f28efe4bfa7ed219601cf00f1a53b7fe7","tid":1377671,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有罷工，可以停止每星期流血衝突！</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"罷工要醞釀能量, 依家比黑警轉移焦點, <br />\n罷工係有用既, 不過要有強大既後盾, <br />\n而似乎呢個後盾要加固, 先可以繼續行落去"},{"pid":"d6f93884e3dc0ea85e9ebeb4c7d472a3c137e639","tid":1377671,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04511772b4d9dfa5055daba756b1382a20e77ab0","tid":1377671,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9405a51f2